{
  "texts": [
    "Regarded jointly, the failure also manifests itself in the inability to realize the goals formulated in the SDGs, which has also been linked to institutional problems.",
    "61 The cause of the failure is also a conceptual flaw, as there is really only one sustainable development goal, namely to achieve all 17 goals without leaving even one behind.",
    "A similar challenge exists with regard to the realization of all international human rights based on the idea of their indivisibility.",
    "62 Ultimately, a similar paradox underlies the current need to regulate AI, which is based on the observation that all humans will be equally affected by AI, albeit in different ways.",
    "Most drastically perhaps, the current global governance problem is visible in the paradox of the Anthropocene."
  ]
}